# 8. 발표에서 쓸 수 있는 문장

결과가 안정적이면:

> The selected AP Tree nodes are relatively stable across testing windows, suggesting that the economic interpretation of the selected characteristic regions is robust.

결과가 불안정하면:

> Although AP Trees are more interpretable than black-box ML models, the selected tree structure is sensitive to the sample period. This weakens the claim that AP Trees provide a stable economic interpretation.

특히 두 지표를 같이 보면 좋아.

> If feature-set stability is high but feature-order stability is low, the same economic characteristics matter across periods, but the conditional ordering of splits is unstable.

이건 아주 좋은 발표 포인트야. 즉:

> size와 value 조합은 계속 중요하지만, size 먼저냐 value 먼저냐는 기간에 따라 달라질 수 있다.

